extends layout

block content
	div.home-nav
		a.link-lg(href="login") Sign In
		a.link-lg(href="register") Register
	hr
	h2 For Users
	div.home-for-users
		div
			h3 Control Your Data
			p See and control exactly what information each service needs and will access when linking to your Xyfir Account.
		div
			h3 Easy Login
			p A couple clicks to authorize a login with a service is all that's needed if you're already logged into your Xyfir Account. No typing!
		div
			h3 Profiles
			p Create multiple profiles with different information for use with linking to different services.
		div
			h3 Ad Profile
			p Control what information is shared across the Xyfir Network and utilized to provide relevant ads for you.
		div
			h3 One Account, Multiple Sites
			p Create one account and access the entire Xyfir Network. Also available are any third party sites that allow login with Xyfir Accounts.
		div
			h3 Manage Linked Services
			p Modify your data for, see what data is being accessed by, and remove services that are linked to your Xyfir Account.
		div
			h3 Security
			p We offer SMS 2-Factor-Authentication, random security codes, IP whitelisting, and more to keep your account secure.
		div
			h3 Passwordless Login
			p Simply enable passwordless login, request an authorization link, and click the link sent to you via SMS or email and you're logged in!
	hr
	h2 For Developers
	div.home-for-devs
		div
			h3 Simple Login
			p Simplify your login system. Let us deal with account management, recovery, security, and so on. Implement our API and be done with it.
		div
			h3 Simple API
			p Create a service, tell us what information your service requires or wants from users, and we'll return it to you upon login or registration.
		div
			h3 Resources / Documentation
			a.link-lg(href="service/dashboard") Create or Manage a Service
			a.link-lg(href="https://xyfir.github.io/accounts") API Documentation